</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149281" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2">You can change a field to regular text, so that it is no longer updated. After you change a field to text, you cannot change the text back into a field.</paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3155608" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">Select the field and choose <emph>Edit - Cut</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3154238" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="9">Choose <emph>Edit - Paste Special</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3154262" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="10">Click "Unformatted text" in the<emph> Selection</emph> list, and then click<emph> OK</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
